散步图

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(sleep,aes(x = extra, y = ID)) +
   geom_point() +
   ggtitle("Student's Sleep Data") +
  xlab("extra") + 
  ylab("ID")

#线图
ggplot(longley, aes(x = Year, y = GNP )) + 
  geom_point() +
  geom_line()

#直方图
 ggplot(pressure, aes(x = pressure )) +
  geom_histogram() 
## `stat_bin()` using `bins = 30`. Pick better value with `binwidth`.

#盒鬚图
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Species, y = Sepal.Length)) +
  geom_boxplot()

#长条图
ggplot(longley, aes(x = Year, y = Employed)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") + coord_flip()
